        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "*Red Hand\u2019s Satchel* is an *alchemist\u2019s haversack*, with a main section containing an extradimensional space like that of a *type IV spacious pouch*.  \n   \nOnce restored, the satchel gains the following activation.",
